{"tid":2348092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又一城示威活動中欲救走男童被控搶犯 男學生獲撤控准守行為","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T15:59:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"022cc135dfdf77b1bc28dcc014284f06ae22cd57","tid":2348092,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"去年11月10日九龍塘又一城有示威活動，一名男童被指破壞「千両」店外配電箱，被警員制服拘捕。其後有男學生嘗試協助男童逃跑，同樣被捕，並遭警方控以一項協助教唆或慫使促致逃離合法羈押罪。案件今日再訊，控方同意以簽保守行為方式結案，主任裁判官羅德泉頒令被告自簽1,000元、守行為24個月，控罪撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，有示威者於又一城「千両」分店閘外噴漆以及破壞店外的配電箱。便衣警員趕至，拘捕一名有份破壞配電箱的男童，為其戴上手銬後要求他坐在店外。其後有記者及示威者共50人上前圍觀，有數名男子隨即襲擊便衣警，男童連忙掙扎嘗試逃跑，其間大叫：「救我！」被告嘗試協助男童掙脫警員，遭另一名警員上前阻止。被告逃跑，及後被制服，警誡下保持緘默。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/WQDTHME45ZGCBFVKYOQ7GG3HIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FWQDTHME45ZGCBFVKYOQ7GG3HIQ%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=e13f0a8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FWQDTHME45ZGCBFVKYOQ7GG3HIQ%2F&h=3c1d0f5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/WQDTHME45ZGCBFVKYOQ7GG3HIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"19453ca6d2c906cdafcdc03822b3d7e8b8b6fe82","tid":2348092,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3e050220c319e26cd1c782345f9f7aa1f2f24c","tid":2348092,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"好明顯咬錯人，如果夠料一定咬到盡"},{"pid":"ce92a0a38d2bd49a5c9f7ce5decbed23a9a74ddb","tid":2348092,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"82a6b3cf65e9ad0f7e525fd7cfa